text: The following lists events that happened during 2011 in the Republic of Equatorial Guinea. ==Incumbents== *President: Teodoro Obiang Nguema Mbasogo *Prime Minister: Ignacio Milam Tang ==Events== ===July=== * July 1 - An African Union summit is held in Malabo with many leaders showing annoyance to the NATO intervention in Libya due to fears of the situation becoming worse. ==References== Category:2010s in Equatorial Guinea Category:Years of the 21st century in Equatorial Guinea Equatorial Guinea Equatorial Guinea
title: 2011 in Equatorial Guinea
